OL,3,CCrews tackling fire at recycling
OL,4,Ccentre at Ashford industrial estate
OL,6,FFirefighters are at the scene of a
OL,7,Flarge fire which broke out at a
OL,8,Frecycling centre in Ashford in Kent.
OL,10,FFire crews were called to Green Box
OL,11,FRecycling at Cobbs Wood Industrial
OL,12,FEstate on Tuesday afternoon. (7 April)
OL,14,FFlames could be seen coming from the
OL,15,Fsite, alongside thick plumes of black
OL,16,Fsmoke.
OL,18,FPeople living near Brunswick Road are
OL,19,Fbeing told to keep doors and windows
OL,20,Fclosed.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
