OL,3,CCrews tackling fire at recycling
OL,4,Ccentre at Ashford industrial estate
OL,6,FA spokesperson for Kent Fire and
OL,7,FRescue Service said: "People living
OL,8,Fnear Brunswick Road in Ashford are
OL,9,Fadvised to keep windows and doors
OL,10,Fclosed due to smoke coming from a fire
OL,11,Fat an industrial waste site.
OL,13,F"Ten fire engines, a height vehicle
OL,14,Fand a bulk water carrier are at the
OL,15,Fscene, and crews are working to
OL,16,Fextinguish the fire."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
